%% The Crucible — Roadmap
timeline
    title The Crucible — Roadmap
    Phase 1 · now : Forge MVP : desktop workspace, Brain v1, knowledge loop end-to-end
    Phase 2 : Local AI : on-device inference for privacy-critical work
    Phase 3 : Team Collaboration : Barrage — shared Mini Brains, scoped permissions
    Phase 4 : Marketplace : shareable Skills, workflows, prompt libraries
    Phase 5 : Enterprise : admin, compliance, auditability, deployment options
